\c 4
\s Ukusola kukaJona lesihawu sikaNkulunkulu
\p
\v 1 Kodwa kwaba kubi kakhulukazi kuJona\x + 1 Sam. 8.6; Jona 4.6.\x*, wathukuthela yena\x + 1 Sam. 15.11.\x*.
\v 2 Wasekhuleka eNkosini, wathi: Ngiyakuncenga, N\nd kosi\nd*, leli lalingesilo ilizwi lami ngiseselizweni lakithi yini? Ngenxa yalokhu ngandulela ngokubalekela eTarshishi\x + 1.3.\x*; ngoba ngangisazi ukuthi wena unguNkulunkulu olomusa\x + Jow. 2.13.\x* lolesihawu\x + Jow. 2.13.\x*\x + Dute. 4.31.\x*, ophuza ukuthukuthela\x + Jow. 2.13.\x*, omkhulu ngothando, njalo ozisola ngokubi\x + Jow. 2.13.\x*.
\v 3 Ngakho-ke, N\nd kosi\nd*, susa, ngiyakuncenga, impilo yami kimi\x + 1 Kho. 19.4.\x*, ngoba kungcono kimi ukufa kulokuphila\x + 4.8.\x*.
\p
\v 4 INkosi yasisithi: Wenza kuhle yini \add ngo\add*kuthukuthela kwakho?
\p
\v 5 UJona wasephuma emzini, wahlala ngasempumalanga komuzi, wazenzela idumba khona, wahlala ngaphansi kwalo emthunzini, aze abone okuzakwenzakala kuwo umuzi\x + Amos 9.11.\x*.
\v 6 INkosi uNkulunkulu\x + Gen. 2. 4.\x* yasimisa umhlafutho, yawukhulisa ngaphezu kukaJona, ukuze ube ngumthunzi phezu kwekhanda lakhe, ukumkhulula\x + 4.7,8; 1.17.\x* kubuhlungu bakhe\x + 1 Sam. 8.6; Jona 4.6.\x*. UJona wasethokoza ngenxa yomhlafutho \add nge\add*ntokozo enkulu.
\v 7 Kodwa uNkulunkulu wamisa impehlane ekuveleni kokusa kusisa, yatshaya umhlafutho, waze wabuna\x + 4.7,8; 1.17.\x*.
\v 8 Kwasekusithi ekuphumeni kwelanga, uNkulunkulu wamisa umoya wempumalanga\x + Jer. 18.17.\x* otshisayo\x + 4.7,8; 1.17.\x*; njalo ilanga latshaya phezu kwekhanda likaJona\x + Hlab. 121. 6.\x*, waze waphela amandla; wafisa emphefumulweni wakhe ukuthi afe\x + Amos 8.13.\x*, wathi: Kungcono kimi ukufa kulokuphila\x + 4.8.\x*.
\p
\v 9 UNkulunkulu wasesithi kuJona: Wenza kuhle yini \add ngo\add*kuthukuthela kwakho ngenxa yomhlafutho? Wasesithi: Ngenza kuhle \add ngo\add*kuthukuthela kwami kuze kube sekufeni\x + Hlu. 16.16.\x*.
\v 10 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi: Wena ube lozwelo phezu komhlafutho ongawutshikatshikelanga, ongawukhulisanga; owaba khona ngobusuku bunye, wabhubha ngobusuku bunye.
\v 11 Mina-ke ngabe kangihawukeli yini iNineve\x + 1.2.\x*, umuzi omkhulu, okuthi kuwo kulabantu abedlula izinkulungwane ezilikhulu lamatshumi amabili abangaziyo \add ukwehlukanisa\add* phakathi kwesandla sabo sokunene lesandla sabo sokhohlo\x + Dute. 1.39.\x*, \add kanye\add* lenkomo ezinengi\x + 3.7.\x*?